```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant DB as Source Database
    participant DMS as AWS DMS
    participant Kafka as MSK/Kafka
    participant Lambda as Lambda Processor
    participant Sink as Data Sink

    DB->>DB: Transaction committed
    DB->>DMS: Read transaction log
    DMS->>DMS: Transform to CDC event
    DMS->>Kafka: Publish CDC event
    Kafka->>Lambda: Trigger processing
    Lambda->>Lambda: Transform & enrich
    
    par Parallel writes
        Lambda->>Sink: Write to S3
    and
        Lambda->>Sink: Write to OpenSearch
    and
        Lambda->>Sink: Write to DynamoDB
    end

    Sink-->>Lambda: Acknowledge
    Lambda-->>Kafka: Commit offset
```
